I attach a copy of advice sent at 6 pm on Friday, 4 Feb 2000 (Australian
Eastern Summer Time), from Dr Gardner Murray, Australian Chief Veterinary
Officer, to Dr Jean Blancou, Director General, of the Office International
des Epizooties, Paris, on the confirmation of virulent Newcastle disease in
a flock of layer pullets near Tamworth, New South Wales, Australia.
Mike Nunn
